InclusionRules.name: Cardiovascular Disease
InclusionRules.description: People either with established cardiovascular disease or who have multiple risk factors for cardiovascular disease

InclusionRules.name: No pregnant women
InclusionRules.description: Patients must not have any pregnancy related concepts between 270 days before and 270 days after the index

InclusionRules.name: No diagnosis of malignancy, cardiomyopathy, cirrhosis, or chronic lung disease
InclusionRules.description: Patients must not have any of the above diagnoses any time prior to the index

InclusionRules.name: No DDP-4 or GLP-1 use
InclusionRules.description: Patients cannot have any DPP-4 or GLP-1 use 6 months prior to the index

InclusionRules.name: No acute cardiac or stroke event
InclusionRules.description: Patients cannot have an acute cardiac or stroke event 2 months prior to the index

InclusionRules.name: No initiation of chronic dialysis or renal transplant
InclusionRules.description: No chronic dialysis, renal transplant, or serum creatinine > 6 all time prior to the index

InclusionRules.name: No diagnosis of HIV
InclusionRules.description: No diagnosis of HIV in all time prior to the index

InclusionRules.name: No autoimmune disorder
InclusionRules.description: Patients cannot have a diagnosis of an autoimmune disorder in all time prior to the index

InclusionRules.name: No concomitant use of oral steroids
InclusionRules.description: Patients cannot be on a treatment of corticosteroids > 30 days

InclusionRules.name: No BMI measurement > 50
InclusionRules.description: Patients must not have any BMI measurement > 50 six months prior

InclusionRules.name: No HbA1c >= 12% in last six months
InclusionRules.description: Patient cannot have an HbA1c >= 12% in last six months

InclusionRules.name: Two BP readings in the past 6 months cannot be > 180/100
InclusionRules.description: Patients cannot have two BP readings > 180/100

InclusionRules.name: No LDL > 250
InclusionRules.description: Patients cannot have an LDL measurement > 250 6 months prior

InclusionRules.name: No HDL < 25
InclusionRules.description: Patients cannot have an HDL measurement < 25 6 months prior

InclusionRules.name: No liver function test > 3 times the upper limit of normal
InclusionRules.description: Patients cannot have a liver function test with a result > 3 times the upper limit of normal 6 months prior
